The late Oba Rauf Olayiwola Adedeji II, Akinrun of Ikirun in Osun State, will be buried today. The late monarch died Wednesday, February 3, 2021 after a brief illness. He was aged 78. Oba Adedeji who came to the throne in July 1991, was a former banker with the defunct Savannah Bank. He will be buried at the Akinrun palace today.